value: A coauthorship network extracted from the DBLP computer science manuscript database, in 2012. This network is a one-mode projection from the bipartite graph of computer scientists and their publications.
['J. Yang and J. Leskovec. \Defining and Evaluating Network Communities based on Ground-truth.\" Proc. IEEE Internat. Conf. on Data Mining (ICDM 2012). arxiv:1205.6233
